Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0}「4月7日  入学仪式和欢迎会」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0}{\fs27}{\an8}春天到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好  小宫起得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  由乃大人不也起得很早吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  是激动得没有睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投在仪式中睡觉一票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭吃了吗  面包可以的话我有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我吃我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  由由  这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是荷包蛋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有翻身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家里翻身是基础的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息日的  真是吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们有开学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是二三年级的人是自由参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是休息日  这么吵很伤脑筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  知道就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘没有告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是从她那里听了很多你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是102室的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  宫子也在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  千英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不知不觉已经这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多时间嘛  冷静地做好准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  文具和重要文件已经放进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕和餐巾纸也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包也拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸？餐巾纸不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子  去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里事情就变得复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  也不用这么紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是山吹高中一直是我憧憬的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在身穿这身校服也非常激动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我穿的话总觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有  一点也不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子  到处都很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  宫子做好出航准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我们出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  今天我们要去开学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订书机没有忘记带上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订书机也需要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘说的话无视就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从上次考试就再也没有进来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欢迎的感觉真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  分班的公告出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫小宫  我们一个班的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个班真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始山吹高中的入学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  首先  请山吹高中校长来致祝词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸  脸好长！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把这份年轻朝气做为武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的话  困死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚开始发麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上本来想好好目送她们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想宫子完全没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我担心那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  早上紧张得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美里学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想看看你们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校叫我趁春假时把一直放在这里的行李拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是入学仪式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得我去老师办公室一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是差不多到结束的时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么我再去挑战一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是呆太久的话  就会难以和你们分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这里随便晃悠  也许可以遇见房东
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  一年级生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  二楼已经两人入住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  要好好对待后辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是谁呢  这不是美里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么怀念向阳庄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}等等  小美里好冷淡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}啊  你干吗要跟过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  不是去学校有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃大人  餐巾纸有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上是谁要我带卫生纸来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我们的教室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  各位  请坐到位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  老师  按照什么顺序坐好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  先随便坐下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  就按照这个位子坐一年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好随便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是班主任吉野屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的一年  请大家都多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始就要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人愿意当裸体模特的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有大家强～烈的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由老师我来代替也没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由要裸体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安结束真是太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本还算平安…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从早上开始神经就一直紧绷着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束后感觉非常放松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好在学校附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由突然就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子背我回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  现在到了宫子的「正确铛挡」的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：正确铛挡，「{\fnTT-JTCウインR7P}{\fs18}ぴったし カン カン{\r}{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}」\N是1975年10月7日～1986年3月18日在TBS每周二播放的\N兼TALK SHOW内容，由明星和观众参加的猜谜节目。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由的体重  「正确铛挡」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下  这是服务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了  芦笋也很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为是无农药的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吃笋饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天要做卷心菜卷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我遇到美里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美里也毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天是邂逅和分离的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然分离让人很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新的邂逅会让人忘记这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是入学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在向阳庄的一年级生有两人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好对待她们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  不过我想我能做的事也不是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小～宫～  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我的信箱里有一封这样的信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给由乃和宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚5点  到弘宅来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能迟到或早到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要空着肚子来!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By  沙英和弘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要上个楼梯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接上来说要方便些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  是现在流行的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然挑我肚子饿的时候  简直卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐…打扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YAHOO  主宾们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然袭击真是卑鄙到了极点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁决！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么的聚会是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的欢迎会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学仪式也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得让你们自己选喜欢的点心和饮料比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要出门买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个子也不出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有让你付钱的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这么说还真是让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门窗都关好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的便利超市Berry Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有  在附近有便利超市真方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在7点就关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把超市里的阿姨叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以买24个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要玩「巧～克～力」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：“巧克力”，从猜拳派生出来的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过宫子出的是石头就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘～草～酸～二～钾～盐～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么适当地选些自己喜欢的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食玩可不算在点心里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把重的行李用力向前甩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能趁这股势头感觉很轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生  恭喜入学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后多多关照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学仪式怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英很担心由乃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天早上简直紧张到不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还好平安结束了  松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仪式中睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长不管是脸还是祝词都太长了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还瑟瑟瑟瑟发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想起了我们那时的入学仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得沙英那时候迟到了一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在仪式开始前我一直和夏目在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目弄错了A班和B班的鞋柜  不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来  我觉得那个时候能很正常地和她交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是从一开始就是那样的态度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有叫做夏目的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  由乃你们哪个班？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A班  我和小宫是一个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是同座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要有认识的人在就觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那运动会的时候  也能在一只队伍里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是根据班级的上下级来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们也是A班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任呢  是个叫吉野屋的女老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有点奇怪的老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  我们的班主任好像会变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  确实是有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说要是拜托她的话连裸体模特也愿意当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后即使不愿意也会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用强行告诉她们我们的成见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  点心的广告？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  膨胀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在一起很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发售了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚在的Berry Mart里没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  已经开始注意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要果汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐的房间真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁纸也给人一种崭新的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  103室和203室是空房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那直到有人住进来为止  能让我用来放放行李吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  随便进去会被骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的房东可是很可怕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃得很饱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚进这里的时候也为我们举办了欢迎会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经成为向阳庄的传统了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地对待后辈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要进行明天的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间布置已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  基本好了  并没有带那么多行李来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也可以买嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  大家每天吃饭是怎么解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己烧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是经常在外面吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢  要送点米过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在达达市场可以便宜地买到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：「免费」和「达达」日文发音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Berry Mart前面的超市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘真好呀  什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常菜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了注意不让沙英营养不良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜的变化就变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家里并没有怎么烧过菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能教我怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:20:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由  你要加油努力多做点好吃的菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这样我就不用担心饭的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  明天的素描要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？弘学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐也找小宫有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好澡后  打个电话给妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月7日  结束  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有听了就想跑步的曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入场曲  交换位置曲  退场曲还有接力赛跑曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白不过我觉得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  就是那个吧  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本是「天堂和地狱」和「邮递马车」还有「威廉·泰尔序曲」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:24:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师听到桑巴就想跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 「10月13日  山上的头目」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在山吹高中等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必要来看哦
